---
title: Pesto Chicken Linguine with peas and Italian style cheese
description: Pesto and pasta... Some might say they make the perfect pairing. The only things that could improve upon this duo of deliciousness are an element of creaminess in the form of creme fraiche and a helping of succulent chicken to round the whole thing out.
